Writership
===
*HEAVILY UNDER DEVELOPMENT*

A state management library, mostly. For UI, game, stateful applications (and servers, hopefully).

Attempt to have:
- A field should only have one mutation/write/change place in code (Writership)
- Easy multithreading without data race thanks to Writership
- Reactive while still imperative (for performance)
- Uni-directional flow
- ...

References:
- https://github.com/rust-lang/rust
- https://github.com/reduxjs/redux
- https://github.com/Microsoft/satcheljs
